category: Audio Video
requires: libmlt2
external-source: mlt
sdesc: "Multimedia framework for broadcasting (C development)"
ldesc: "MLT is an open source multimedia framework, designed and 
developed for television broadcasting. It provides a toolkit for 
broadcasters, video editors, media players, transcoders, web streamers 
and many more types of applications. The functionality of the system is 
provided via an assortment of ready to use tools, XML authoring 
components, and an extensible plug-in based API."
